scene.name: Battle of Mollwitz
scene.description: The Battle of Mollwitz was fought by Prussia and Austria on 10 April 1741, during the First Silesian War.

prussia.name: Kingdom of Prussia
prussia.description: The Kingdom of Prussia was a German kingdom that constituted the state of Prussia between 1701 and 1918.

habsburg.name: Habsburg monarchy
habsburg.description: The Habsburg monarchy was the collection of lands and kingdoms of the Habsburg dynasty.

frederick.name: Frederick II
frederick.description: He was King in Prussia from 1740 until 1772, and King of Prussia from 1772 until his death.

schwerin.name: Kurt Christoph von Schwerin
schwerin.description: He was a Prussian Generalfeldmarschall, one of the leading commanders under Frederick the Great.

kalckstein.name: Christoph Wilhelm von Kalckstein
kalckstein.description: He was a Prussian field marshal on May 24, 1747.

marwitz.name: Heinrich Karl von der Marwitz
marwitz.description: He was a Prussian infantry general and military governor of Breslau.

posadowsky.name: Karl Friedrich von Posadowsky
posadowsky.description: He was a Prussian lieutenant general, head of the Dragoon Regiment No. 1 and the Knights' Academy in Liegnitz.

schulenburg.name: Adolph Friedrich von der Schulenburg
schulenburg.description: He was a lieutenant general in the Prussian army and confidante of King Friedrich Wilhelm I of Prussia.

leopold.name: Leopold II. Maximilian
leopold.description: He was the reigning Prince of Anhalt-Dessau from the Ascanian family and at the same time a Prussian general.

neipperg.name: Wilhelm Reinhard von Neipperg
neipperg.description: Count Wilhelm Reinhard von Neipperg was an Austrian general.
